me.armar.plugins.autorank.requirementhandler
Class RequirementHandler

java.lang.Object
  me.armar.plugins.autorank.requirementhandler.RequirementHandler

public class RequirementHandler
extends java.lang.Object

RequirementHandler will keep track of the latest known group and progress a player made (via /ar complete) When the last known group is not equal to the current group of a player, all progress should be reset as a player is not longer in the same group. RequirementHandler uses a file (/playerdata/playerdata.yml) which keeps tracks of these things.

Author:
Staartvin
